PrecisAppointment of ROBERT ANDRIGO as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Latvia, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Estonia; STEFANIE BECK as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Cambodia; ADAM BLACKWELL as Ambassador of Canada to the Dominican Republic; ANNE CHARLES as Consul General of Canada at Chicago (United States of America); ALLAN CULHAM as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Venezuela; JEAN-MARC DUVAL as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Colombia; DAVID HUTTON as Ambassador of Canada to the United Arab Emirates; JAMES LAMBERT as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Guatemala, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of El Salvador; PAUL LAU as High Commissioner for Canada in Brunei Darussalam; GILBERT LAURIN as Deputy Permanent Representative and Ambassador of Canada to the United Nations; MICHAEL LEIR as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Turkey, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Georgia and to Turkmenistan; RALPH LYSYSHYN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Poland; DONALD McLENNAN as Ambassador of Canada to the Federal Republic of Yugoslavia; MARK MOHER as Ambassador of Canada to Ireland; VALERIE RAYMOND as High Commissioner for Canada in the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Maldives; JEAN-MICHEL ROY as Consul General of Canada at Dallas (United States of America); JOHN SCHRAM as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Zimbabwe; CHRISTOPHER THOMSON as Consul General of Canada at Minneapolis (United States of America); and JAMES WALL as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Kenya; and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the United Nations Centre for Human Settlements in Nairobi; and as Permanent Representative of Canada to the United Nations Environment Program in Nairobi.
